## MIDI channel reference

POMSKI uses 0-indexed channels (`channel=0` = MIDI ch 1).

| Channel | Use |
|---------|-----|
| 0–8, 10–15 | Melodic instruments |
| 9 | GM percussion |

Template slots `ch1`–`ch16` map to channels 0–15 respectively.
